Text.Value: Hang on... High Harper Jaheira?! Saviour of Baldur's Gate? Incredible.
I'm not familiar with that name. A Harper leader, perhaps.
The name sounds familiar. A Harper leader, if I recall.
Cultists... threat to Baldur's Gate... Jaheira's orders...

EditorData.NodeContext: Jhaam is his name. Pronounced Zhahm.

Text.Value: Jaheira? Can't say I know the name.
Last Light... safe haven... in shadows...
Hmmm, that name doesn't ring a bell.

EditorData.NodeContext: Jhaam is his name. Pronounced Zhahm.

Text.Value: *The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*
The name sounds familiar - I hope we didn't meet on one of my little excursions.
*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*
*The corpse seems willing to speak - but not to its killer.*

Synopsis: Player finds drow corpse hanging in a cage in Grymforge. When you click on it you discover that it was a Harper who came here, and could get some foreshadowing about Last Light and the name Jaheira.
